                        <interp inst="t18421024-name-1079" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MARSHALL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable B</hi> 60.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
